                            <p class="text-break white-space-pre-line">Salary: Negotiable depending on skills and experience. Experience The successful incumbent will work within the Butchery and must possess at least two (2) years experience within a position as a cashier. Formal qualifications Matric or equivalent NQF level A valid driver's licence Responsibilities The incumbent will be responsible for: Processing sales transactions Accepting payments (cash, POS or account) Calculating and returning change when required Maintaining adequate change in the cash register Answering questions from customers regarding products Reporting issues with equipment Working as a team to meet sales targets Handling customer complaints Maintaining a clean and tidy working area and checkout area Assisting in rotating stock Weighing items with correct codes Scanning and bag items efficiently and accurately Inherent requirements for the position Efficiency Good time management Due diligence Excellent communication skills Commercial awareness Enthusiasm, patience and perseverance Flexibility and versatility Attention to detail Good problem-solving skills Reliable and dependable with sober habits Attention to accuracy and detail Analytical Shortlisted candidates will be expected to undergo psychometric testing and background screening. Applicants who fulfil the abovementioned requirements are invited to apply for the position by following the link: https://www.placementpartner.co.za/wi/adverts.php?idmultiform and registering your application on-line. Applications which are done by means of email or fax will not be considered. For more information, an email may be sent to nandimultiform.co.za</p>
